{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2166820/extras/\u6807\u9898\u6309\u94ae4X.png?t=1719511920\" /><br><br>&quot;Slime\u00a0warfare&quot;\u00a0is\u00a0a\u00a0roguelike,\u00a0strategy\u00a0and\u00a0tower\u00a0defense\u00a0game.\u00a0A\u00a0special\u00a0tower\u00a0defense\u00a0game\u00a0where\u00a0you\u00a0can\u00a0freely\u00a0build\u00a0roads\u00a0and\u00a0rich\u00a0buff\u00a0towers.\u00a0Players\u00a0take\u00a0on\u00a0the\u00a0role\u00a0of\u00a0Queen\u00a0Slime\u00a0against\u00a0invading\u00a0adventurers.<br>This is a non-traditional tower defense game. You need to cleverly arrange the enemy's attack path and the position of the tower. The numerical advantage formed by the buff tower can allow you to win the game without external reinforcement.<br><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Slimes\u00a0and\u00a0Adventurers</h2></strong><br><br>Legend has it that slimes are very weak creatures. This is a struggle between slimes and adventurers. Eliminate the invading adventurers to defend slimes! Save the slime queen, unlock characters and portraits. Each character has different values \u200b\u200band mechanisms.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2166820/extras/juese.png?t=1719511920\" /><br><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Core Selection</h2></strong><br><br>Each battle has? ? Core selection. Each core will change your game mode.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2166820/extras/\u6838\u5fc31.png?t=1719511920\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>BUFF\u00a0Tower</strong></h2>Buff tower is the highlight of this game. You can use BUFF tower to strengthen your queen or attack tower to achieve the game clearance. You can also use traditional tower defense layout without using buff tower.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2166820/extras/20240628-012450.gif?t=1719511920\" /><br><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">planning</h2></strong><br>Unlike\u00a0previous\u00a0tower\u00a0defenses,\u00a0the\u00a0attack\u00a0towers\u00a0here\u00a0have\u00a0HP.\u00a0So\u00a0plan\u00a0the\u00a0layout\u00a0and\u00a0defend.\u00a0The\u00a0same\u00a0type\u00a0of\u00a0tower,\u00a0placed\u00a0in\u00a0different\u00a0positions\u00a0will\u00a0even\u00a0determine\u00a0your\u00a0success\u00a0or\u00a0failure.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2166820/extras/20240628-012403.gif?t=1719511920\" /><br><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">free\u00a0road</h2></strong><br><br>In\u00a0the\u00a0game\u00a0you\u00a0can\u00a0pave\u00a0your\u00a0own\u00a0path.\u00a0According\u00a0to\u00a0the\u00a0progression\u00a0of\u00a0each\u00a0game\u00a0time,\u00a0you\u00a0can\u00a0get\u00a0the\u00a0number\u00a0of\u00a0road\u00a0grids\u00a0you\u00a0can\u00a0lay.\u00a0During\u00a0the\u00a0game,\u00a0you\u00a0can\u00a0change\u00a0the\u00a0layout\u00a0of\u00a0the\u00a0road\u00a0at\u00a0will\u00a0to\u00a0assist\u00a0your\u00a0strategy.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2166820/extras/20240628-012131.gif?t=1719511920\" /><br><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">random\u00a0and\u00a0decision</h2></strong><br>Choose\u00a0the\u00a0tower\u00a0you\u00a0need\u00a0from\u00a0randomly\u00a0drawn\u00a0towers.\u00a0You\u00a0can\u00a0choose\u00a0attack\u00a0towers\u00a0to\u00a0increase\u00a0your\u00a0attack\u00a0units,\u00a0or\u00a0you\u00a0can\u00a0choose\u00a0buff\u00a0towers\u00a0to\u00a0strengthen\u00a0your\u00a0attack\u00a0units.<br><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Enhanced\u00a0upgrade</h2></strong><br><br>If you can't beat it, you can choose to upgrade your attack tower and queen in the main interface to protect every dungeon.<br>(If you like challenges, you can pass the level without upgrading off-site.)","achievements":{"highlighte